                    <h2>Community</h2>
                    <h4>Support</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Documentation: <a href="http://electrum.readthedocs.org/">http://electrum.readthedocs.org</a></li>
                        <li>Official announcements are made on <a href="../twitter.com/ElectrumWallet.html">Twitter</a></li>
                        <li>You can ask questions on <a href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?board=98.0">bitcointalk.org</a></li>
                        <li>As well as on <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Electrum/">Reddit</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Development</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>IRC channel: <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/electrum">#electrum</a> channel on Freenode</li>
                        <li>Bug reports: <a href="../github.com/spesmilo/electrum.html">electrum page on GitHub</a></li>
                        <li>Localization: <a href="https://crowdin.net/project/electrum">https://crowdin.net/project/electrum</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Electrum Servers</h4>
                    <ul>
			<li>Server source code: <a href="https://github.com/kyuupichan/electrumx">ElectrumX</a> (new, faster implementation)</li>
                        <li>How to run your own Electrum server: <a href="https://github.com/kyuupichan/electrumx/blob/master/docs/HOWTO.rst">Install Guide</a></li>
			<li><a href="https://1209k.com/bitcoin-eye/ele.php">Servers list and status</a> (Lists only Bitcoin Electrum servers)</li>
			<li><a href="https://bohol.petrkr.net/electrum-stats.php">Statistics from Petrkr's server</a>
                    </ul>

